	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=308433><span id= >Brohg</span></a><br><span id=notbold>12 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [5.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>increases proc rates of weapons. base proc rate is 100, and equates to 2 proc's per minute, over time.&nbsp;&nbsp;various weapons have different bases, the summoned cleric hammers are a good example. they're something like 650 as a base, if I remember right. They proc about 13 times/minute.  Less dramatic differences are the Bloodfrenzy and Darkblade of the Warlord, warrior weapons.  The have base proc rates of 130 or 160 or something, I really don't remember.<br><br>So that's what Combat Effects +s do, add to that base and make weapons 'go off' more. It's an AMAZING modifier for warrior gear, because of how it boosts their agro generation over time.  It's also quite a RARE mod, do a search :P</p>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
